what_worked: Applied or_to_union, intersect_to_exists, multi_date_range_cte: Split the query into focused CTEs for date_dim, item, and inventory filters, then used EXISTS semi-joins instead of full joins to catalog_sales and inventory to avoid cross-join expansion.
why_it_worked: Converting OR to UNION ALL lets optimizer choose independent index paths per branch; Replacing INTERSECT with EXISTS avoids materializing full intermediate sets; Separate CTEs for each date alias avoids ambiguous multi-way date joins
